data.name: lblMessage.Text
data.value: Drive to the player at the location indicated on the Tow Ticket. Be sure to read the description, if provided, to ensure you bring all of the proper tools. The player who submitted this Tow Ticket will mark this Ticket as complete when you have finished. IMPORTANT: When the Tow Ticket is complete, return the Tow Truck and key to location you picked it up.
